title: #116: TWA 800 and The Secret Society of Eagle Scouts with Ray Kump
description: Welcome to another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  This show we welcome from the Tim Dillion Is Going To Hell Podcast, Ray Kump, to discuss the secret world of Eagle Scouts, Flight 800, The Titanic and 9/11. Thank you so much for listening and we appreciate your support!
